  "content": "\n \n \n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\">\n        <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"246\" data-backw=\"578\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb3Ilo96uLxX6C3VGN2lZQADeVFEDzcHDI70rqmWOqOWBGic7fT8ydnjejSCdjNO0dFHOZV8E10UHsA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-imgfileid=\"505106393\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/58bb1703-0e71-48c3-18c1-ea8ee4b3dd00/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/58bb1703-0e71-48c3-18c1-ea8ee4b3dd00/public\"></span>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\">\n   <span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：英智</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">大模型之战烽火正酣，谷歌Gemini 2.5 Pro却强势逆袭！Gemini Flash预训练负责人亲自揭秘，深挖Gemini预训练的关键技术，看谷歌如何在模型大小、算力、数据和推理成本间找到最优解。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">谷歌凭借Gemini 2.5 Pro在激烈的大模型竞争中一举翻盘。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">近日，Geimini Flash预训练负责人Vlad Feinberg在普林斯顿大学分享了相关内容。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他深入分析了Gemini预训练的方法、挑战以及方向，如何在模型大小、算力、数据和推理成本间取得平衡。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"313\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"948\" data-imgfileid=\"505106397\" data-ratio=\"0.5576470588235294\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4a033ced-e038-41e1-7664-a918e60f3700/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1700\" data-width=\"1700\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4a033ced-e038-41e1-7664-a918e60f3700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"ma0vun8gzyh\" data-mpa-action-id=\"ma0vun9429u\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">PPT链接：https://vladfeinberg.com/assets/2025-04-24-princeton-talk.pdf</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">经典扩展定律</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">模型训练中，计算资源的合理利用至关重要。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">假设有计算资源（C）1000块H100芯片，运行30天，如何训练出最佳的LLM呢？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这就涉及到模型参数量（N）和训练token数量（D）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于Transformer，计算量C和N、D之间存在一个近似公式：C≈6×N×D。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ba45dd91-2c42-4a54-cae8-52c7c20ce900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4337957124842371\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1586\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1586\" data-height=\"688\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"244\" data-imgfileid=\"505106399\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ba45dd91-2c42-4a54-cae8-52c7c20ce900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">MLP是模型的重要组成部分，不同操作的浮点运算量和参数量有所不同。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">比如</span><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2bca4a0a-059e-469c-a34a-f21476aa2500/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.13882532418001525\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1311\" style=\"width:168px;height:23px;\" data-width=\"1311\" data-height=\"182\" data-imgfileid=\"505106396\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2bca4a0a-059e-469c-a34a-f21476aa2500/public\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这个操作，训练时的浮点运算量是6BTDF，参数量为DF。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">把MLP的多个操作加起来，总训练浮点运算量约为18BTDF，参数数量达到3DF。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">注意力机制的计算更为复杂。将注意力机制相关操作的计算量相加，约为12BTSNH=12BT²NH，参数量为4DNH。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">将MLP和注意力机制的计算量合并，就能了解整个模型训练时的计算量情况。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e8cdb12e-23c7-4a3c-9240-c4c752487800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e8cdb12e-23c7-4a3c-9240-c4c752487800/public\"></span></strong></p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Kaplan定律</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2020年，Kaplan等人的研究揭示了模型性能与数据量、模型规模和计算量之间的关系。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">自回归Transformer模型中，小模型可以用来预测大模型的性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">模型性能与算力、参数量、数据量之间存在幂律关系。当计算预算增加10倍时，模型参数量应增加5.37倍，数据量增加1.86倍。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一结论在当时引起了广泛关注，点燃了企业的「军备竞赛」。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/27665fa5-08a6-4846-6a96-1ba634b78200/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5951283739302172\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1519\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1519\" data-height=\"904\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"335\" data-imgfileid=\"505106400\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/27665fa5-08a6-4846-6a96-1ba634b78200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e8cdb12e-23c7-4a3c-9240-c4c752487800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e8cdb12e-23c7-4a3c-9240-c4c752487800/public\"></span></strong></p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Chinchilla（龙猫）</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，2022年，DeepMind对Kaplan的观点提出了质疑。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/deb66dca-79a5-4d2b-a6fd-292300a34300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.48749237339841367\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1639\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1639\" data-height=\"799\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"274\" data-imgfileid=\"505106398\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/deb66dca-79a5-4d2b-a6fd-292300a34300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Kaplan的研究在每个模型规模下仅运行一次训练，并用中间损失来估计不同token训练步数下的损失。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Chinchilla论文指出，基于单次训练的中间loss点来推断存在缺陷，通过适当的学习率衰减可以获得更好的损失值，只有最终的损失值才是最优的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">论文采用IsoFlops方法，固定浮点运算量预算，同时改变模型规模和训练token数量。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"ma0vv42t106r\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">固定总算力C</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">训练多个不同参数N的模型，对应不同数据量D（C≈6×N×D）</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">找到loss最低的模型N_opt（C）和D_opt（C）</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"ma0vv42tx4a\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">重复以上步骤，得到不同算力下的最优（N,D）点，并拟合</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6b52b62f-df71-4606-b54d-14515103ea00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.517304189435337\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1647\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1647\" data-height=\"852\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"291\" data-imgfileid=\"505106401\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6b52b62f-df71-4606-b54d-14515103ea00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究发现，模型参数N和数据量D应以大致相同的速率（幂律指数约为0.5）随算力C增长，这与Kaplan等的结论大相径庭。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这意味着，按Kaplan定律训练的模型，可能存在训练不足的情况，数据太少，会增加模型后续部署和使用的成本。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6b6feee0-61e1-46da-ef6d-9bb0718b2c00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.47601246105919004\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1605\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1605\" data-height=\"764\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"267\" data-imgfileid=\"505106402\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6b6feee0-61e1-46da-ef6d-9bb0718b2c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了进一步优化模型训练，研究人员尝试了多种方法。通过不同的计算场景和拟合方式，得到了更精确的系数。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">混合专家（MoE）模型的扩展定律展现出了独特的优势。与传统模型相比，在相同的活跃参数数量和固定100B token的情况下，MoE 64E模型的性能更优。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/71935b5f-95ac-4207-0ae8-ed3ed92b4e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5127445168938944\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1687\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1687\" data-height=\"865\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"288\" data-imgfileid=\"505106405\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/71935b5f-95ac-4207-0ae8-ed3ed92b4e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，MoE模型对token数据的需求量较大，互联网上的可用数据逐渐难以满足其需求，这成为了发展瓶颈。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了解决数据不足的问题，研究人员将目光投向了更多的数据来源。多模态数据，如音频、视觉、3D 模型、视频等，为模型训练提供了丰富的信息。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">合成数据也受到了关注。实际应用中，需要在生成质量与筛选成本之间找到平衡。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">实时场景的模型选择</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在谷歌的许多应用场景中，如免费的Gemini聊天机器人、AIO、AIM、Vertex AI（用于模型微调、部署）以及AI Studio（提供生成式API）等，推理效率至关重要。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这些应用需要快速给出准确的响应，对模型的推理速度和效率要求极高。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">就拿实时应用来说，Astra和Mariner都需要快速响应。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">以一个网络交互智能体为例，假设上下文128k，但每次增量只有8k token，解码需要128 token来生成一个动作，并且动作之间的延迟不超过1秒，其中250毫秒还得用于框架搭建、负载均衡等操作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">用Llama3-70B模型和v5e芯片做实验，发现单芯片处理8k token需5.7秒。为了达到0.5秒的API延迟限制，需要搭建4×4 v5e并行。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">实时应用中，小模型反而更有优势，如Gemini Flash/Flash-lite。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/20456213-9eb9-40a5-7204-73ff56415b00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5990961910910265\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1549\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1549\" data-height=\"928\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"337\" data-imgfileid=\"505106406\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/20456213-9eb9-40a5-7204-73ff56415b00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Chinchilla的扩展方法虽然在模型训练的计算优化上有效，但它忽略了推理成本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在实际应用中，需要综合考虑训练和推理的成本，找到更合适的模型和数据配置。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">推理优化扩展定律</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">《超越Chinchilla最优：在语言模型扩展定律中考虑推理因素》这篇论文提出了新的推理优化Scaling Laws。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">核心思想是，不仅最小化训练loss，而是要综合考虑训练和推理的总计算量，为模型优化提供了新的方向。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/20013e80-eece-499e-4e57-902d4e730e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.553763440860215\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1674\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1674\" data-height=\"927\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"311\" data-imgfileid=\"505106404\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/20013e80-eece-499e-4e57-902d4e730e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">按照这些公式，在相同计算量下，与Chinchilla最优策略相比，应该训练更小的模型，并使用更多的数据，因为推理所需的计算量更少。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当然，这也存在新的挑战。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">计算资源的非同质性</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：实际应用中计算资源存在差异，用于推理优化的芯片各不相同，给推理优化带来了困难。</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">推理量D_inf难以预测</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：技术进步提高资源利用效率，反而会增加对该资源的需求（杰文斯悖论）。模型质量提升可能会扩大市场，进而影响推理时的token数量D_inf。</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">拟合效果不佳</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：不同数据集下，相关参数的拟合效果存在差异。不同token与参数比例的数据子集，拟合得到的 α、β等参数不同，和Chinchilla的拟合结果也有较大差异。</span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">针对这些问题，研究人员采用在数据约束下建模的方法。研究引入新维度，即有意区分数据，提出新的损失函数和数据规模公式，这样训练出来的模型更小，对数据重复的鲁棒性更强。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/77d5558d-225e-43a7-d14c-a188c5017800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4733009708737864\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1648\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1648\" data-height=\"780\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"266\" data-imgfileid=\"505106407\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/77d5558d-225e-43a7-d14c-a188c5017800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于推理token数量的处理，像Llama3模型，有研究指出其8B和70B参数的模型，在训练到15T token后，性能仍呈对数线性提升，即D_inf可视为无穷大。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">蒸馏的探索与应用</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">除了模型大小、数据量和推理成本，知识蒸馏为推理优化扩展带来了新的思路。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">知识蒸馏扩展定律公式：</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2b146301-59cb-4a7c-57c5-ca58481fdb00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.13429752066115702\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1452\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1452\" data-height=\"195\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"75\" data-imgfileid=\"505106409\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2b146301-59cb-4a7c-57c5-ca58481fdb00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">通过调整这些参数，可以优化学生模型的性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不过，知识蒸馏在实际应用中也有一些问题，比如趋势影响不明显、部分情况考虑不周全等，但可以通过权重调整等方法进行改进。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从原理上讲，知识蒸馏能降低方差，更好的教师模型能减少偏差，为模型优化提供了新途径。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">谷歌Gemini预训练技术对经典扩展定律和推理优化扩展定律都进行了深入研究。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">经典扩展定律通过探索模型规模、数据量和计算量之间的关系，不断优化模型训练的资源配置。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">推理优化扩展定律针对推理成本和效率问题，综合考虑训练和推理需求，提出新方法，提升模型整体性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">同时，知识蒸馏等技术的应用也为模型的优化提供了更多的途径。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"ma0vw8zlre2\" data-mpa-action-id=\"ma0vw8zx98d\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Vlad Feinberg</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/36db5095-ebfc-4781-0508-b7730d917300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6670792079207921\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"808\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"808\" data-height=\"539\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"375\" data-imgfileid=\"505106408\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/36db5095-ebfc-4781-0508-b7730d917300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Vlad Feinberg毕业于普林斯顿大学计算机科学专业，于加州大学伯克利分校RISE实验室攻读博士学位。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">后来，Feinberg加入了一家名为Sisu的初创公司，担任机器学习主管。他曾任职于谷歌研究院的Cerebra项目，目前在谷歌DeepMind工作。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://x.com/JeffDean/status/1916541851328544883</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://x.com/FeinbergVlad/status/1915848609775685694</span></span></section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "谷歌 Gemini 预训练负责人揭秘了 Gemini 在资源分配和推理优化策略上的关键技术，以在模型大小、算力、数据和推理成本之间寻找最优解。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "谷歌 Gemini 预训练负责人揭秘了 Gemini 在资源分配和推理优化策略上的关键技术，以在模型大小、算力、数据和推理成本之间寻找最优解。",
  "summary": "文章深入探讨了谷歌 Gemini 预训练的关键技术，重点分析了在模型训练中如何在模型大小、算力、数据和推理成本之间取得平衡。谷歌 Gemini 2.5 Pro 凭借其独特的预训练策略，在性能上实现了显著提升。文章回顾了经典的扩展定律，如 Kaplan 定律和 Chinchilla scaling，并介绍了谷歌在推理优化扩展定律上的研究进展，该定律为在实际应用中选择合适的模型大小和数据量提供了指导。此外，文章还探讨了混合专家模型（MoE）的优势与挑战，以及知识蒸馏在模型优化中的应用。最后，文章还分析了在实际应用场景中，如何根据推理效率选择合适的模型，如 Gemini Flash/Flash-lite 等小模型，这些小模型在实时应用中具有显著优势。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "经典扩展定律（如 Kaplan 和 Chinchilla）为模型训练提供了资源配置的指导，但存在一定的局限性，例如忽略了推理成本。",
      "explanation": "Kaplan 定律和 Chinchilla scaling 等研究揭示了模型性能与算力、参数量和数据量之间的关系，为模型训练提供了重要的参考，但这些定律在推理成本方面存在局限性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "推理优化扩展定律综合考虑了训练和推理成本。",
      "explanation": "与 Chinchilla 最优策略相比，推理优化扩展定律提倡训练更小的模型，并使用更多的数据，以降低推理所需的计算量。"
    },
    {
      "point": "知识蒸馏为模型优化提供了新的途径。",
      "explanation": "通过调整知识蒸馏相关参数，可以优化学生模型的性能，降低方差，并利用更好的教师模型减少偏差，从而实现模型优化。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "模型性能与算力、参数量、数据量之间存在幂律关系。当计算预算增加 10 倍时，模型参数量应增加 5.37 倍，数据量增加 1.86 倍。",
    "按 Kaplan 定律训练的模型，可能存在训练不足的情况，数据太少，会增加模型后续部署和使用的成本。",
    "不仅最小化训练 loss，而是要综合考虑训练和推理的总计算量，为模型优化提供了新的方向。"
  ],
